HEADWORD: bloviate
<hw>blo"vi*ate</hw> <pr>(bl⟦omac⟧"v⟦icr⟧*⟦amac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>bloviated</conjf>
